content:
The authentication pattern for Android apps integrated with Marketing Cloud Engagement is changing. 
To send push notifications to Android devices after this date, admins must upload the Service Account JSON file for each active Android app before June 1, 2024.
This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions and uploads must be complete by June 1, 2024.
Admins can upload Service Account JSON files in the Administration tab of MobilePush.
title: Update Android App Authentication for Marketing Cloud Engagement
